rspec_xml_validation_matchers
=============================

Setup
------

Dependencies:
-------------

  * rspec
  * rspec_on_rails
  * libxml

Overview
--------

Adds a conform_to_dtd matcher that takes an path to an XSD file as it's parameter.

Usage
-----

describe User do
  before do
    @user = User.new
  end

  it "should create xml that conforms to the xsd" do
    @user.to_xml.should conform_to_dtd('user.xsd')
  end
end

